notes
PIs of the SP: Keisuke Hosokawa (UEC)
We will conduct radar observations of pulsating aurora using the EISCAT UHF system (scanning mode like 
ip2-mode) to investigate polarization electric field associated with pulsating aurora. We prefer good weather 
condition for simultaneous optical observations.

